        <item>
            <title>張家朗 IG 被意大利人洗版鬧偷金牌　意大利劍擊聯盟為賽果提抗議</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/30/cheungkalong-ig-spam-by-italian/hottopic/spotlight/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=cheungkalong-ig-spam-by-italian</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/30/cheungkalong-ig-spam-by-italian/hottopic/spotlight/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2024 06:23:32 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[城中熱話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[運動科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[2024 巴黎奧運]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[張家朗]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1253662</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">香港劍擊選手張家朗今日成功在 2024 巴黎奧運的男子花劍個人項目再度奪金，是花劍 68 年歷史以來首次有劍手成功衞冕金牌。不過張家朗在決賽面對的意大利劍手馬治（Filippo Macchi）和他的團隊卻對賽果感到不滿，認為他被剝奪了應得的金牌，意大利劍擊聯盟亦表明會向國際劍聯及國際奧委會提出抗議。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1253670 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/mfile_1763780_1_2024-e1722318392232-626x580.jpg" alt="" width="626" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/mfile_1763780_1_2024-e1722318392232-626x580.jpg 626w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/mfile_1763780_1_2024-e1722318392232-972x900.jpg 972w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/mfile_1763780_1_2024-e1722318392232.jpg 1451w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 626px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1763780-20240730.htm">RTHK</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">張家朗在花劍決賽中與對手馬治難分難解，多次出現比數追平的情況，直到最後出現「決三劍」的情況下張家朗成功以 15:14 勝出。其中最爭議的地方就在於「決三劍」，來自台灣的國際裁判在頭兩次的判決中均判定了需要重打，直到第三次才判決張家朗取得決勝分勝出賽事。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="it" dir="ltr">Filippo Macchi argento per incompetenza.<br />Oro per l&#39;intervista post partita.<br />Oro pure a Stefano Cerioni come c.t.<a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Macchi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Macchi</a><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Cerioni?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Cerioni</a><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/fencing?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#fencing</a><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Olimpiadi?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Olimpiadi</a><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/Olympics?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#Olympics</a><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/OlimpiadiParigi2024?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#OlimpiadiParigi2024</a><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/olimpiadi2024?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#olimpiadi2024</a><a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/OlympicGames?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#OlympicGames</a><a href="https://t.co/99YM5x6b1S">pic.twitter.com/99YM5x6b1S</a></p><p>&mdash; eletizia (@chiamamimirella) <a href="https://twitter.com/chiamamimirella/status/1818035952310485124?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">July 29, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p style="font-weight: 400;">意大利劍擊聯盟質疑兩位分別來自台灣和南韓的裁判質素不符合比賽水平，又指有裁判是來自香港的鄰近地區，認為任何情況下裁判都不會是來自鄰近的國家或地區。香港前花劍代表張小倫同樣認為裁判的判決有問題，他提到幾劍都是張家朗佔上風，而且判決只會是其中一方成功得分，而不可能是重打。他認為裁判的判決很猶豫，對兩位劍手都會造成很大的影響。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="wp-image-1253665 size-medium aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2097-320x580.jpg" alt="" width="320" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2097-320x580.jpg 320w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2097.jpg 496w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 320px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class=" wp-image-1253673 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2100-694x218.jpg" alt="" width="523" height="164" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2100-694x218.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2100.jpg 1170w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 523px" /></p><figure id="attachment_1253674" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1253674" style="width: 485px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1253674 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2101-485x580.jpg" alt="" width="485" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2101-485x580.jpg 485w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2101.jpg 752w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 485px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1253674" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲意大利網民在張家朗 IG 上洗版攻擊</span></figcaption></figure><p>其實不只馬治和他的團隊對賽果感到不滿，戰線更轉移至網絡上。不少意大利網民在賽果一出後，紛紛湧到張家朗的 Instagram 帳户中「洗版」，攻擊張家朗偷走了他們的奧運金牌。他們在張家朗的 IG 留下了「以他為恥」、「偷走了奧運獎牌」、「依靠法國教練關係取勝可恥」等的惡意留言。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1253677 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2102-316x580.jpg" alt="" width="316" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2102-316x580.jpg 316w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2102.jpg 490w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 316px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1253678 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2103-317x580.jpg" alt="" width="317" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2103-317x580.jpg 317w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2103.jpg 492w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 317px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class=" wp-image-1253679 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2104-586x580.jpg" alt="" width="343" height="339" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2104-586x580.jpg 586w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2104.jpg 909w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 343px" /></p><figure id="attachment_1253666" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1253666" style="width: 318px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-1253666 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2099-e1722318023373-318x580.jpg" alt="" width="318" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2099-e1722318023373-318x580.jpg 318w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2099-e1722318023373-494x900.jpg 494w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_2099-e1722318023373.jpg 1168w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 318px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1253666" class="wp-caption-text"><span style="font-size: 10pt; color: #000000;">▲香港網民以「菠蘿 Pizza」還擊</span></figcaption></figure><p style="font-weight: 400;">當然香港網民不會放任自己的選手被人這樣攻擊，大多數支持張家朗的網民都認為意大利團隊輸打贏要，挺身向張家朗表示支持並用上意大利人最討厭的菠蘿披薩「🍍」、「🍕」Emoji 還擊。但都有網民勸停有關的留言還擊，避免為張家朗的成功沾上污點。</p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://www.i-cable.com/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E8%B3%87%E8%A8%8A/%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2/254424/?utm_source=facebook_cable_news&amp;utm_medium=facebook_link_organic&amp;utm_campaign=share&amp;fbclid=IwY2xjawEVTdlleHRuA2FlbQIxMAABHRGoW4fbn3sEB-C6hGJigUXQ3Z4kCxHp7X8pZskpuyYG5pOyoZ0KwV6-Wg_aem_NTrm20IyfZ6qrtmi-c-7Qw">有線新聞</a></span></p><p>圖片來源：<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1763768-20240730.htm">RTHK</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/22/summer-olympics-apple-maps-update/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple Maps 推出更新，為巴黎奧運揭幕作準備</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/30/cheungkalong-ig-spam-by-italian/hottopic/spotlight/">張家朗 IG 被意大利人洗版鬧偷金牌　意大利劍擊聯盟為賽果提抗議</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
