            <title>中國擬簽發實名「網號」「網證」　宣稱可保護個人資料安全</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/29/chinese-real-name-2024/tech-secure/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=chinese-real-name-2024</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/29/chinese-real-name-2024/tech-secure/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 12:00:28 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新聞]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[資訊保安]]>
